text: Eunidia albolineatipennis is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Stephan von Breuning in 1968.BioLib.cz - Eunidia albolineatipennis. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Eunidiini Category:Beetles described in 1968
